reviewText: Can't believe I am giving a Peter Cushing movie a low rating, but his brief contribution could not save this movie. Is so cheesy and full - could have been better. Tedious to watch. But others may like it.
Great suspenseful movie that keeps you on the edge!
A must for the classic Hammer lover!  Peter Cushing is all that one might expect him to be and the ending is classic Hammer-twisted!

ok, but video was grainy NOT what I consider a remastered DVD.

No subtitle.

No extras.

The story wasn't that good so can't recommend a buy unless you're collecting Peter Cushing movies.
